		text-align: left;
	}
	.div3{
		height:150px;
	}
 }
</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="font_div">
		<div class="div1">
			<span>POSITIONS & MOVEMENTS</span>
		</div>
		<div class="div2">
			<div class="hr_left_div2"></div>
			<div class="hr_center_div2">FEATURE 8</div>
			<div class="hr_right_div2"></div>
		</div>
		<div class="div3">
			<div style="height:5%;"></div>
			<div class="hr_top_div3"></div>
			<div class="hr_middle_div3">
				<div style="height:30%;"></div>
				<span id="des0">&nbsp;&nbsp;All the positions and movements of all types of assets are covered in clear reports.</span>
				<span id="des1" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;包括账户列表</span>
				<span id="des2" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;通知书/邀请函</span>
				<span id="des3" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;投资组合摘要</span>
				<span id="des4" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;投资组合列表</span>
				<span id="des5" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;资产配置</span>
				<span id="des6" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;货币账户</span>
				<span id="des7" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;股票</span>
				<span id="des8" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;以及证券动态</span>
				<span id="des9" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;外汇汇率</span>
				<span id="des10" style="display:none;">&nbsp;&nbsp;电子结单</span>
			</div>
			<div class="hr_bottom_div3"></div>
		</div>
